</screen>
</para>

<para>
 Dernæst skal du som systemadministrator installere pakken:
<screen>
<prompt>[tyge@hven ~]$ </prompt><userinput>su -c 'make install &amp;&amp; /sbin/ldconfig &amp;&amp; echo O.k.'</userinput>
Password:
